Package: simpleHM
Type: Package
Title: Create ggplot2 based Heatmaps
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Jasper", "Spitzer", email = "spitzer@uni-bonn.de",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9696-2092"))
Description: The package is designed to build heatmaps, mostly in the context of high-troughput data.     
    It utilises the tidyverse packages heavily and returns a ggplopt object, with all the functionality that comes with it.
